# ==============================================
# NewsBrief AI — Environment Variables
# ==============================================
# 
# DO NOT commit the real .env file to Git!
# This file (.env.example) is just a TEMPLATE.
#
# Steps:
# 1. Copy this file and rename it to: .env.local
# 2. Fill in your real API keys below
# 3. When deploying to Vercel, add these as
